<lb n="0077b19" ed="J"/><cb:juan n="2" fun="close"><cb:jhead>印心佛敏訥禪師語錄卷第二<note place="inline">終</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0077b20" ed="J"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pJ37p0077b2001" style="margin-left:8em">板存嘉興楞嚴般若堂流通</p></cb:div>
